# GitBandit Environment Variables Template
# Instructions: Copy this file, rename it to .env, and replace the placeholder values with your actual data.
# WARNING: Do NOT commit your actual .env file to version control bozo!!!

# Your GitHub Personal Access Token (PAT)
# To generate one:
# 1. Go to GitHub -> Settings -> Developer Settings -> Personal access tokens -> Tokens (classic)
# 2. Generate a new token and ensure you check the 'repo' scope (Full control of private repositories).
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_personal_access_token_here